e safety, and hygiene. This action follows a report highlighting numerous PGs operating without proper permits, posing risks to public health and safety within residential areas.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/hospitality/bengaluru-to-crackdown-on-unauthorised-pgs-and-hostels-starting-november-12/125268283?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-157742/125268283.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "hospitality"}]}